    a(href="https://twitter.com/CarrieRosePR" target="_blank") Carrie Rose
    |!{' '}is the co-founder of!{' '}
    a(href="https://riseatseven.com/" target="_blank")
      span.italic Rise at Seven
    | , a creative SEO agency.
  p Over the last year I’ve been consistently blown away by how easy she makes getting press look.
  p And it’s not!{' '}
