    | .
  p The reward is high quality backlinks which help her clients rank for!{' '}
    span.bold ultra-competitive
    |!{' '}search terms.
  h2.under Lets start with an example
  p
    span.italic Missguided
    |!{' '}is a fashion retailer who started working with!{' '}
    span.italic Rise
    |!{' '}last year.
  p Carrie looked at their site for 5 minutes, saw they sold dog jumpers, and knew there was a story there.
  p So she found some similar looking regular jumpers, and wrote the headline:
  p.inwardSpeech Missguided launch matching jumpers for you and your dog this winter
  img(src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/harrydry/gdmarketing/carrie1.jpg" alt="Marketing Examples Product Hunt").img__100
  p The media loved it. The campaign pulled in!{' '}
    span.bold 80
    |!{' '}links. And!{' '}
    span.italic Missguided
    |!{' '}soared from!{' '}
    span.bold #30
    |!{' '}to!{' '}
    span.bold #1
    |!{' '}for the search “dog jumpers”.
  p No big budget or photoshoot. Just!{' '}
    span.italic the idea
    |!{' '}to link two pre-existing products with a clever headline.
